def: A mild kind caustic used to reduce warts and otherexcrescences. Dunglison.
One of a tribe of Amphibia, which have both lungs and gills atthe same time, as the proteus and siren.

An enlargement, or series of enlargements, in the anterior partof the alimentary canal, in which food is digested; any cavity inwhich digestion takes place in an animal; a digestive cavity. SeeDigestion, and Gastric juice, under Gastric.
A polymeric modification of terpene, obtained as a whitecrystalline camphorlike substance; -- called also camphene. Byextension, any one of a group of related substances.
Dark and threatening; gloomy; sullen; as, lowering clouds orsky.
A light-colored highly effervescent beer made by the top-fermentation process.
Uncharitableness. Tennyson.'T were much uncharity in you. J. Webster.
